2008-03-09  Carlos Garnacho  <carlosg@mate.org>

	* Release 2.22.0

2008-02-28  Carlos Garnacho  <carlosg@mate.org>

	* caja/caja-shares.c (file_get_share_status_file): remove
	wrongly placed g_return_if_fail on an uninitialized variable. Fixes
	#519295 (Vincent Untz).

